{"name":"分析性思維（Analytical Mind）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　分析思維是邏輯性分析資訊，推導問題解決方案或從干擾中分離出重要資訊的不可思議的能力。常用來破解密碼、解決謎題、找出陷阱和數據篩選。這個特質賦予角色＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整到任何涉及模式識別、證據分析、線索搜尋、解決謎題的邏輯檢定中。這個特質也會讓角色解決問題的時間減半。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"078r4DqjtsFkFrnE"}
{"name":"社會壓力（Social Stress）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　無論是因失去親友、心理創傷，還是先天性心理缺陷所致，社會壓力劣勢都會在情感上成為角色社交的障礙。選擇該劣勢的角色需指明原因及觸發條件。舉例來說，如果他的社會壓力源自於失去朋友后獨自倖存的愧疚感，若與某個相貌和死去的朋友很像的人不期而遇，將會令他壓力大增。當角色在使用領導或儀禮技能時，檢定中出現失誤所需<span lang=\"EN-US\">１</span>點骰的個數相應減少<span lang=\"EN-US\">１</span>個。<span lang=\"EN-US\">GM</span>應當給具有社會壓力的角色更多社交檢定以確認角色對待他人的反應，特別是在可能誘發角色社會壓力的情況下。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 87"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"0RQII0NFYQiN1WQA"}
{"name":"程式碼阻塞（Codeblock）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有程式碼阻塞特質的角色總是在一種特定的矩陣行動中遇到麻煩。他在任何時候嘗試該矩陣行動都會獲得<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整。程式碼阻塞僅適用於有相關檢定的矩陣行動，不適用無需檢定的行動（<span lang=\"EN-US\">P237</span>）。不可能進行黑入行動的角色不能選取這個特質。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 82"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"0uqmMz0UtU60Tcce"}
{"name":"精魂導師（Mentor Spirit）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　每個人在其一生中都需要一些幫助，即使來自某個比較朦朧虛幻的傢伙。精魂導師特質意味著角色跟隨著一位守護精魂（見〖精魂導師〗，P. 320），在他的魔法實踐中引導他並給他的天生能力帶來一些優點和缺點。角色可以改變精魂導師，但他在同一時間只能擁有一個精魂導師。改變精魂導師，角色首先必需如同購買負面特質一樣將現有精魂導師驅除。他可以稍後再次購買這個特質以遵循不同的精魂導師。這個花費是離開一位精魂導師並與另一位精魂導師聯結的代價。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　精魂導師在不同流派中有不同的名字。赫爾墨斯法師稱其為「精魂導師」，薩滿則稱他們遵循的精魂為「圖騰」。雖然名字不同，但導師運作的方式是相同的。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\">　　只有擁有魔法屬性等級的角色能夠選擇這個特質。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 78"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"236ADwhE2lBsbCiQ"}
{"name":"喪失信心（Loss of Confidence）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　喪失信心特質說明有什麼東西導致角色對他自己和他的一項能力喪失了信心。比如說，角色可能是一個很熟練的碟客，但是他在侵入雜貨店的主機時依然失敗了；或者儘管角色有著一個很高的敏捷，他也在簡單的攀爬檢定中出現失誤並摔了下來。無論何種原因，他現在懷疑他自己和他的能力。涉及受影響的技能檢定時，角色承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整。如果角色專精這個技能，角色在喪失信心時不能享受專精的好處。角色選擇受到喪失信心影響的技能必須是角色建立的時候購買過的。只有等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>或更高的技能能夠承受喪失信心的影響。當角色喪失信心時，這個技能不能使用極限點。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 84"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"5MHK3fhoJjZ24qgs"}
{"name":"天生免疫（Natural Immunity）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　隨便喝毒藥都不會中招的能力。擁有天生免疫的角色與生俱來或是後天發展出對一種疾病或毒素的免疫。</p>\n<p>　　這個特質有兩級可選。如果購買<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>業力的等級，角色免疫一種天然疾病或毒素。如果在天生免疫上購買完全<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力的等級，角色免疫一種合成（人工製造）的疾病或毒素。</p>\n<p>　　天生免疫對基於魔法的疾病或毒素無效，比如<span lang=\"EN-US\">HMHVV</span>。</p>\n<p>　　玩家和ＧＭ必須在角色免疫何種疾病、毒品或毒藥上達成一致。角色可以每六個小時攝取一劑毒品、毒藥或暴露一次在疾病傳染中而沒有任何不良影響。在隨後的六小時內，任何劑量和暴露都如常造成傷害，但角色的恢復時間減半。</p>\n<p>　　注意，擁有天生免疫的角色可能會成為疾病攜帶者，在其本人不受疾病影響的同時可能會感染其他角色。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 78"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"5qYYhViSxoKmT8c6"}
{"name":"攝影記憶（Photographic Memory）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有攝影記憶的角色可以瞬間回憶起具體事實、日期、數字或任何其所見所聞。角色在所有記憶檢定上獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 78"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"5r3hASf6gJ6ZefZD"}
{"name":"優越屬性（Exceptional Attribute）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　優越屬性特質就是你如何成為有魅力的巨魔和敏捷的矮人的原因。它允許你將一項屬性最高上限提高一點。例如，一個在力量上擁有優越屬性特質的獸人角色可以在安裝改造之前將力量屬性提升至<span lang=\"EN-US\">９</span>，以代替正常上限的<span lang=\"EN-US\">８</span>。優越屬性也適用於特殊屬性，如魔法和共鳴。極限不受優越屬性的影響（極限提升通過另一種被稱為幸運的特質）。角色只能選取一次優越屬性特質，並且需要得到ＧＭ的批準。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"5w8D7LAntMIoHsUl"}
{"name":"幸運（Lucky）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　扔骰子和拋硬幣是這個角色更常選擇的方式，這讓她有機會因為自己的好運氣驚掉下巴。幸運允許角色最大極限屬性＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>（比如說，一個人類角色可將她的極限提高到８）。注意，選取這個特質並不會實際提升角色的當前極限等級，這只是給予她機會這樣做而已；獲得額外定數的業力花費依然需要支付。這個特質僅能選取一次並需得到ＧＭ的批準。幸運特質不能與優越屬性同時選擇。這個特質會使惡名-1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 78"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"6693ITbUo9wM8dVy"}
{"name":"看似人類（Human-Looking）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　一個擁有看似人類特質的泛人類角色可以在大多數情況下像人類一樣。當進行社交技能檢定時，人類<span lang=\"EN-US\">NPC</span>會以中性的態度迴應角色，即使這些人類對泛人類抱有偏見。角色可能會承受那些對人類抱有偏見的泛人類<span lang=\"EN-US\">NPC</span>更多的仇視，他們要麼將其誤認為人，要麼就是懷疑他看似人類的動機。只有精靈、矮人和獸人可以選取看似人類特質。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 77"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"6vPJiH0h8WgmYCyJ"}
{"name":"自家地盤（Home Ground）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　如果角色比任何人都瞭解她的左鄰右舍，捷徑、藏身處以及她可以信任的人，那她很可能擁有自家地盤特質。她瞭解住在這裡的家庭，他們的故事，哪個孩子搬出去在做什麼事；她比地圖指南更瞭解這些街道，知道那些甚至地圖指南都不知道的事情，知道什麼時候地圖指南出錯。她瞭解幫派政治，誰為誰狂奔，誰是誰的狂奔目標。但這不僅限現實街道。角色的自家地盤特質可以以特定的方式體現，取決與她是誰，她幹什麼的。當選取這個特質時，從如下獎勵中選擇一項：</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">適應星界（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Astral Acclimation</span>）</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">角色在其自家地盤上適應了星界背景輻射。通過一生的熟悉，她學會了如何在其中工作，使得她忽略至多２點背景輻射。例如，如果她在自家地盤上的背景輻射為３，她的魔法檢定只會承受１點罰值；如果背景輻射為５，對她來說罰值就只有３，以此類推。這個特質只在她自家地盤上有效，在其他地方沒有任何好處。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">你認識人（<span lang=\"EN-US\">You Know a Guy</span>）</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">這個角色和她的鄰居建立起了長期關係。這些人不是人脈，但是他們將角色視為他們的一員，很可能有利於她或和她交談。角色自家地盤上的<span lang=\"EN-US\">NPC</span>鄰居在哪裡遇見她都對她視為友好狀態（除非她做了什麼事改變了這點）。角色在與自家地盤上的任何人的談判中獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>街頭信譽。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">數字化領域（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Digital Turf</span>）</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">這是碟客或超鏈者聲稱其所有一臺特定主機。她可能事實上擁有自己的地點，或是足以被稱為家的地方。當角色在自家地盤的主機上時，她在矩陣檢定中獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>加值。從其他特質上獲得的加值可以與自家地盤的加值疊加。如果角色沒有光顧這臺主機長達六個月，她失去自家地盤特質，因為她不再像她應該的那樣熟悉這個地方了。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">運送者（<span lang=\"EN-US\">The Transporter</span>）</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">角色對街頭巷尾瞭如指掌。當地圖指南出錯或過期時，她會知道。當運送者在她的自家地盤時，她在〈追擊/甩開〉載具檢定上獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。當嘗試一開始避開跟蹤時，潛行檢定也會獲得+2骰池調整。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">潛逃中（<span lang=\"EN-US\">On the Lam</span>）</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">躲藏和保持低調是一個暗影狂奔者的日常生活。潛逃中意味著角色擁有關於安全屋、藏身處、廢棄建築的百科知識，幾乎所有不會被幫派成員或鳩佔鵲巢者注意到的偏僻之地。當她需要緊急地找到一個安全的位置時，這個角色在用於快速找到合適的地方的直覺＋相應街頭知識技能上獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池獎勵。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">街頭政治（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Street Politics</span>）</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">這個角色瞭解街頭幫派、犯罪活動和表面之下的聯繫，也就是她自家地盤上的社會和政治結構。她在有關幫派和他們的活動的知識檢定上獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">　　這個特質可以選擇多次，每次從上述內容中選擇不同類別。</span></p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 76"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"7fafRxByB9BkemTV"}
{"name":"過敏（Allergy）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　擁有過敏特質的角色對環境中的某種物質或處境過敏。這個特質的量值基於兩個因素。首先，該物質或處境是不常見（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>業力）還是常見（<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>業力）。其次，過敏癥狀的程度：輕度（<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>業力），中度（<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>業力），重度（<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>業力）或極度（<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>業力）。將適當的數值相加得到最終值。例如，不常見中度過敏（銀）是<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>業力）。如果角色被用他們過敏的物質攻擊，他們的過敏每嚴重一層其抗力檢定就失去<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>顆骰子（例如，輕度過敏失去<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>顆骰子，中度過敏失去<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>顆骰子等等）。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"width: 598pt;\" border=\"0\" width=\"797\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\"><colgroup> <col style=\"width: 15pt; mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 640;\" width=\"20\" /> <col style=\"width: 54pt;\" span=\"2\" width=\"72\" /> <col style=\"width: 460pt; mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 19616;\" width=\"613\" /> <col style=\"width: 15pt; mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 640;\" width=\"20\" /> </colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 36pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl71\" style=\"height: 36pt; width: 598pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" colspan=\"5\" width=\"797\" height=\"48\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffc000; font-size: x-large;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"colo