f2f2f2;\">2</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl77\" style=\"width: 460pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"613\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">該物質或處境在本地環境中很罕見。例如：銀、金、抗生素、草。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl67\" style=\"width: 15pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"20\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">　</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 37.5pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"height: 37.5pt; width: 15pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"20\" height=\"50\">\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">　</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl84\" style=\"border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; width: 54pt; border-bottom: #ffcc00 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: #262626;\" width=\"72\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">常見</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl85\" style=\"border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; width: 54pt; border-bottom: #ffcc00 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: #262626;\" width=\"72\">\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">7</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl86\" style=\"border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; width: 460pt; border-bottom: #ffcc00 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: #262626;\" width=\"613\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">該物質或處境在本地環境中是普遍存在的。例如：陽光、海鮮、蜜蜂、花粉、污物、WiFi敏感、大豆、小麥。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl67\" style=\"width: 15pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"20\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">　</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"height: 21pt; width: 15pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"20\" height=\"28\">\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">