{"name":"程式碼玩家（Codeslinger）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　一和零才是玩程式碼的真正母語。角色熟練于執行特定矩陣動作（當她選擇這個特質時選定），他獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整在這個矩陣動作上。為這個特質選擇的矩陣動作（<span lang=\"EN-US\">P237</span>）必須是需要進行檢定的。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"BqrJRD5GK4ojKqhL"}
{"name":"歧視（Prejudiced）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　擁有這個特質的角色對特定群體的成員懷有歧視，比如泛人類、覺醒者、非泛人類智慧生物或其他人。角色不僅僅是不夠寬容，他對自己堅信的事情毫無避諱並且會積極反對他歧視的目標。根據歧視的程度，這種特質讓角色表達自己的觀點或面對自己歧視的目標時陷入麻煩。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　這個特質的業力獎勵取決於角色仇視的群體有多常見，他有多大的可能遭遇他們，以及他會公開對抗他們的可能有多大。參見「歧視表」根據角色仇視的群體的普遍程度和其歧視程度決定特質獎勵的業力值。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　當和他們歧視的目標打交道的時候，角色的歧視特質每有一級嚴重程度就要在所有社交檢定上獲得<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整。如果談判是遭遇的一部分，角色的歧視特質每有一級嚴重程度，目標就獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>調整。所以如果角色激進地歧視覺醒者而嘗試和覺醒者談判的話，他們在談判檢定上獲得<span lang=\"EN-US\">－6</span>同時對方獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>骰池調整。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"width: 407pt; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"542\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\"><col