ottom: #ffc000 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: black;\">\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"color: #ffc000;\"><strong>業力值</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl69\" style=\"height: 18pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"24\">　</td>\n<td class=\"xl77\" style=\"background-color: #404040; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">偏見（如秘密的泛人類仇視者）</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl73\" style=\"width: 56pt; background-color: #404040; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"75\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">0</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl69\" style=\"height: 18pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"24\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">　</span></td>\n<td class=\"xl75\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">不避諱（如人類主義者的典型成員）</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl72\" style=\"width: 56pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"75\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">2</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl69\" style=\"height: 18pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"24\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">　</span></td>\n<td class=\"xl76\" style=\"border-top: #