{"name":"天資（Aptitude）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　這個特質表明了你是如何做到強中更強的。技能的標準上限是<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>級。偶爾有些角色可以超過限制，他的一個特定的技能達到真正的卓越。擁有這個特殊的特質，角色在角色建立時可以有一個技能達到等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>，並可以最終提升到等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>。角色只能選擇此特質一次。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"CiNPcW2qWCsy1nVN"}
{"name":"小魔怪（Gremlins）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：每等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>業力（最大<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>級）</p>\n<p>　　擁有小魔怪特質的角色和那些科技玩意處得不太好。莫名其妙的裝置故障，令人意外的軟體崩潰，無法啟動的載具，他接觸的部件異常脆弱，他參與的無線鏈接受到奇怪的干擾。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"left\">　　當角色試圖使用一個稍微尖端一點的裝置時，每級「小魔怪」（最大<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>級）使出現〖失誤〗的閥值－１。例如，一個骰池為<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>、２級「小魔怪」（<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>業力）的角色，在檢定中骰出兩個或更多<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>（代替正常的四個）就會失誤。ＧＭ可以要求角色為一些原本可以自動成功的操作進行檢定，以決定是否出現失誤。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"left\">　　當決定「小魔怪」引起的失誤效果時，ＧＭ應該具備特別古怪的機械或電子裝置故障的概念。「小魔怪」引起的失誤例子包括：當試圖用手槍重擊時，彈倉掉了出來；當進入程式碼解除報警系統時，鍵盤莫名燒了起來；當試圖通過受限節點時，通訊器介面變成了不成句的賽普瑞希爾語。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"left\">注意，「小魔怪」是個負面特質，它阻礙了角色（可能娛樂了他人）。角色無法以「小魔怪」特質僅僅通過接觸去損壞敵人的高科技裝置。該角色任何通過「小魔怪」去蓄意破壞的裝置都將功能完美。（顯然，他可以嘗試傳統的破壞方式，但小魔怪會影響他的努力。）</p>\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"left\">　　這個效果只適用於外部裝備而不影響賽博改造、生體改造或其他植入。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 83"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"D6JvJOLQEP2SAV7w"}
{"name":"不屈不撓（Indomitable）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：每等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>業力（最大<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>級）</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　肉體和精神都有極限，但有些人擁有一直超越這些限制。不屈不撓特質上每有一個等級，角色在他選擇的一個固有界限（精神、肉體或社交）上獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>的提升。他至多可以以任意分配方式提高三級（例如，一個固有界限＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>或者一個固有界限＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>、另一個＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>再或者三項都＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 77"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"DMRC0lJDQS4iKdWP"}
{"name":"膽量（Guts）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　當口流涎水的甲蟲精魂突然現身，擁有膽量的角色是最可能屹立反擊而非嚇得屁滾尿流的。膽量給予角色在對抗恐懼和威嚇時＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整，包括法術或生物能力導致的魔法性恐懼。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 76"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"HIfCvFVRO7CUILZR"}
{"name":"獨特風格（Distinctive Style）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有獨特方格特質的角色至少在外貌、言談、舉止、個性的一個方面使其難以讓人忘懷。可選獨特風格包括卻不限於以下方面：不易遮掩的紋身，不常見的說話方式或口音，怪異的時尚選擇，疤痕，幫派或監獄標誌，可笑定製植入體或比如一條尾巴這樣非泛人類的裝飾。注意在一種文化或地方獨特的東西在另一種文化或地方則未必獨特。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　無論玩家為她的角色選擇怎樣容易記住的獨特風格。任何試圖識別、跟蹤或物理定位這個角色（或通過調查獲得其資訊）的相關檢定獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。如果<span lang=\"EN-US\">NPC</span>要通過記憶檢定（<span lang=\"EN-US\">P152</span>）來確定他回憶多少關於角色的事情，難度閾值減<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>，最小為<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　這個特質天然的，不適用于星界搜索。這個特質只能被選取一次。這個特質與低調特質衝突。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 82"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"JnNRWQLHL7licB4V"}
{"name":"沒文化（Uneducated）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　一個角色沒文化並不意味著她在智力上有缺陷&mdash;&mdash;她只是沒得到學習的機會。不論是因家庭被孤立、身份未經認證，還是因其它原因導致社會地位低下，她都被教育體系所拒絕。她只有閱讀、寫作與算術的基礎知識。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　沒文化的角色對於那些他們不具備的〈專業技能〉、〈學術知識〉和〈專業知識〉技能視作無知水平（見技能等級，第<span lang=\"EN-US\">129</span>頁），他們不能進行未受訓檢定。即使是那些對外城區人來說習以為常的事情，<span lang=\"EN-US\">GM</span>也可以要求角色為其進行檢定。此外，用以學習/提升這些新技能/技能組/專精的業力花費是通常情況下的兩倍（包括角色建立環節；特指業力，不包括技能點的使用），且角色可能永遠也學不到這些類別下的某些技能組。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 89"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"Jo55QnTYNmGTMfK0"}
{"name":"成癮（Addiction）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　擁有成癮特質的角色迷上了化學物質（街頭毒品：<span lang=\"EN-US\">novacoke, bliss, tempo</span>）、技術或魔法裝置（更好的生活晶片（<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>）或法器）或者潛在的成癮行為（賭博或性）。生理成癮影響人體機能，造成疼痛、噁心、顫抖以及其它會損害狂奔者的副作用，尤其是在戒斷的時候。心理成癮的一些可能影響包括偏執、焦慮、失眠、注意力不集中、情緒障礙和抑鬱。成癮檢定、戒斷檢定以及脫癮的特定規則詳見〖成癮規則〗P. 414。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　這個特質的獎勵業力取決於成癮的嚴重程度。成癮程度包括：輕度、中度、重度和極度。長時間不進行治療，成癮就會惡化。成癮特質的每個等級都有起始劑量等級，告知角色他們必需要多少量才能滿足。如果角色有植入體，這個等級可能還會提升。角色成癮越嚴重，滿足慾望所需的物質或進行活動的時間就越多。</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　成癮特質程度較弱時（輕度、中度），更容易隱藏成癮的影響。較為嚴重的程度下（重度、極度），就會有明顯的成癮生理或心理跡象。這些跡象對他的社交檢定造成負面影響，即使他沒有承受戒斷效果。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">輕度（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>業力）<span lang=\"EN-US\">/1</span>劑量或<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>小時嗜好活動</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">角色的輕度慾望一個月出現一次。如果角色在戒斷檢定中失敗，他就要承受戒斷癥狀並且會積極尋找使用該物質或進行相關活動以尋求解脫。在狂奔中，這可能意味著推遲狂奔者團隊一起為工作精心設計的計劃，尤其是角色忙於賽馬的賭博或沉溺<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>而沒有進行狂奔時。當角色承受戒斷癥狀時，在角色所有基於精神屬性的檢定上受到骰池－<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>調整（心理依賴）或者在角色所有基於肉體屬性的檢定上受到骰池－<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>調整（身理依賴）。如果角色在戒斷檢定中成功，直到角色的下一次戒斷檢定之前（一個月），角色不會承受戒斷癥狀並且不需要相關物質或嗜好活動。他在這個月很「乾淨」。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">中度（<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>業力）<span lang=\"EN-US\">/1</span>劑量或<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>小時嗜好活動</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">角色的中度慾望每兩週出現一次。如果經受戒斷，他在所有基於精神屬性的檢定上（心理依賴）或所有基於肉體屬性的檢定上（生理依賴）承受－<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>，直到慾望滿足。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">重度（<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>業力）<span lang=\"EN-US\">/2</span>劑量或<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>小時嗜好活動</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">這種成癮已經失控。該慾望每週都要經歷一次。如果他在戒斷檢定上失敗，他在戒斷中基於精神屬性或基於肉體屬性的檢定上承受－<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>骰池調整（根據其依賴而定）。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.3pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">另外，他在所有社交檢定上承受－<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整，無論其是否在戒斷狀態中。角色現在沒有辦法完全隱藏他的成癮癥狀，即使當他剛過過癮之後也是如此。他成癮導致的傷害的生理和心理跡象很容易被近處的觀察者看到。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt 21.3pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 21.3pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 21.25pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">極度（<span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span>業力）<span lang=\"EN-US\">/3</span>劑量或<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>小時嗜好活動：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">極度成癮是這個特質的最終狀態。藥物或習慣的慾望每天都會出現。除非他們用相應的物質或活動滿足慾望，否則角色在戒斷中基於精神屬性或基於肉體屬性的檢定上（取決於他們的依賴）承受－<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>的罰值。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">　　因為他成癮的狀態是如此明顯，即便是最漫不經心的觀察者也會注意到。無論是否處於戒斷狀態，角色在所有社交檢定上承受－<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>骰池調整。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\"> <span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">　　ＧＭ決定是否需要成癮角色在不進行遊戲的時候進行戒斷檢定，取決於ＧＭ想要成癮對角色的遊戲體驗造成多大的影響。</span></p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 79"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"MfdLXoX11FtlPJ90"}
{"name":"求生意志（Will to Live）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：每等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>業力（最大<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>級）</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt;\">求生意志上每有一個等級，角色就能承受多一點溢出傷害（<span lang=\"EN-US\">P. 101</span>）。這些額外點數只是讓角色死亡前承受更多的傷害；它們不能提升角色變得無意識或無行為能力的閾值，也不影響角色的傷勢調整值。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 79"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"OGOmCL8d8K43uFFu"}
{"name":"星界變色龍（Astral Chameleon）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　擁有星界變色龍特質的角色，其星界印記（astral signature）混入了星界空間的背景中從而難以偵測。這個角色留下的所有星界印記的持續時間減半。任何人通過星界感知檢定感知擁有這個特質的角色留下的混合星界標識都會承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整。只有擁有魔法等級並能夠留下星界印記的角色可以擁有這個特質。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"PPW0LvEQOzg1PWvB"}
{"name":"低調（Blandness）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　這個角色能夠輕易混入人群，他很少被注意到也很容易被遺忘。他的外表的每個方面都是毫不起眼的。任何試圖描述這個角色的人都沒法找到比「普通身高、普通身材、普通頭髮」等更精確的語句來進行形容。</p>\n<p>　　任何人想要回憶起這個角色的特定細節，檢定閾值提高<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>。這意味著記憶檢定從普通（閾值<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）變得困難（閾值<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>）。</p>\n<p>　　試圖在人口稠密的環境中跟蹤或物理定位擁有低調特質的角色要在所有搜索相關的檢定上承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整。如果基於其外表四下打探這個人要承受相同的懲罰。然而，通過魔法或矩陣搜索時不適用這個懲罰。如果角色有任何可見的紋身、疤痕、明顯的賽博改造或其他便於識別的特徵，低調特質帶來的加值會取消直到角色外表的鮮明特徵移除掉。</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　在某些環境和特定情況下，ＧＭ可以決定低調特質不適用。例如，一個擁有低調特質的巨魔，無論他的犄角多麼普通，其高大的身軀依然會讓他在一群人類中鶴立雞群。角色只要在離開了這種使其突顯的環境后才能獲得他的加值。此外，這個特質會使惡名-1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"QB1tK6pTQSKNYVLF"}
{"name":"裝作獸人（Ork Poser）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　受到地精搖滾或誇張獸化趨勢的影響，裝作獸人就是一個精靈或人類角色將自己的外貌改變得像一個獸人一樣。各種各樣生物改造&mdash;&mdash;獠牙種植、類固醇、喉部改造等等&mdash;&mdash;這使得他成功地像獸人一樣。裝作獸人對很多獸人來說令人尷尬，但也有些獸人對此保持容忍，即便不欣賞，也承認他們的努力。這意味著當獸人發現角色的秘密既可能變得非常敵視他也可能願意讓角色加入「家庭」，通過一個適當的惡作劇來證明自己的「獸人性」。一個被揭露的裝作獸人也可能面臨被其他人類或精靈視為「種族叛徒」，如果這些人類或精靈懷有對獸人的偏見。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　只有人類和精靈可以選取裝作獸人特質。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 84"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"QfatJ5uA04r2SAE3"}
{"name":"精魂親和（Spirit Affinity）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　精魂親和特質只有魔法使用者可選，允許角色與一種型別的精魂調諧（見精魂，p. <span lang=\"EN-US\">303</span>）。這些精魂對該角色感興趣，更傾向於幫助她。他們可能不願攻擊該角色，如果迫不得已也會盡量採取非致命力量。窺探者（Watchers）和其他小鬼（Minion）不受這個特質影響，因為他們是被構造的而不是像普通精魂一樣被召喚的。對於有精魂親和的魔法師而言，他能從每個與其調諧的精魂那裡獲得額外１個精魂服務，並在束縛檢定上獲得＋１骰池調整。</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　魔法使用者在這個特質上選擇的精魂型別可以不屬於他們的魔法流派。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 79"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"QzEv2xF4Agb6Q5B6"}
{"name":"敏感系統（Sensitive System）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有敏感系統特質的角色對賽博植入有著免疫抑制方面的問題。賽博改造的精華損失將會翻倍。而且無論生體植入是如何成長和設計的，它們都會被角色肉體所排斥。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　對於那些永遠不會考慮植入的浮現（Emerged）或者覺醒（Awakened）角色而言，這個特質會產生不同的作用。一個魔法使用者或超鏈者仍然有著引導魔力或利用共鳴的完整能力，但他們更容易受到潛在的耗竭或衰褪的影響。一個擁有「敏感系統」的魔法使用者或超鏈者在進行任何耗竭或衰褪檢定之前，必須進行一個檢定，意志（2）。這個檢定的失敗意味著，接下來的耗竭或衰褪檢定中的耗竭或衰褪值＋2，他們的敏感系統使得能量流經他們的身體時造成了更多的傷害。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 85"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"ShfSDJUNexsFhxrX"}
{"name":"魔法抗力（Magical Resistance）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：每等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>業力（最大<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>級）</p>\n<p>　　這是個能夠彈開火球術的奇妙能力。在魔法抗力上每花費<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>業力，角色在法術抗力檢定中就獲得<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>顆額外的骰子。然而魔法抗力特質始終「開著」，角色不能降低它以接受如治癒術這類有益法術。擁有魔法抗力的角色不能參加需要自願目標的法術；這樣的法術使用在魔法抗力的角色身上時自動失敗。</p>\n<p>　　擁有魔法等級的角色不能選取這個特質。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 78"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"TmSywARS3Rr7AcXY"}
{"name":"強韌（Toughness）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有強韌特質的角色比別人更容易對傷害置之不理。當進行傷害抵抗檢定時，角色獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>骰池調整到他們的體質上。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 79"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"U6d4MAbWda3Pa6RT"}
{"name":"天生硬化（Natural Hardening）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　這個特質使得角色的天生結構更能抵抗反饋。這給予了她<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>點天生生物反饋過濾，這與生物反饋過濾程式或超鏈者的防火墻（p. 251）疊加。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 78"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"VC6vya8F4FzTMnhc"}
{"name":"擬感暈眩（Simsense Vertigo）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　每當經歷增強現實、虛擬現實或擬感裝置（包括數碼鏈接、模擬裝置，及影像鏈接）時，擬感暈眩的角色就會陷入定向障礙（即，一種對時間、地點或鑑別力的精神錯亂狀態）。這樣的角色在進行任何與增強現實、虛擬現實或擬感相關的檢定時，都將受到<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 85"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"VOCGmmk7oqO5q6c8"}
{"name":"鬼祟如貓（Catlike）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　一個擁有鬼祟如貓特質的角色具備不可思議的優雅、隱匿的步伐、無聲移動的超常能力的天賦。他們墜落時也能安靜落地，即使他們往往不會讓別人有機會嘗試。這個特質給予潛行技能檢定＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"VdgKZrxtOt7N6nFm"}
{"name":"至愛親朋（Dependents）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有至愛親朋特質的角色有一個或多個所愛之人依賴於他們的情感支援和經濟援助。至愛親朋包括子女、父母、配偶或情人、兄弟姐妹或者一個老朋友。滿足至愛親朋的需要得佔用角色一些時間以及金錢。學習新技能或提升已有技能需要額外百分之五十的時間。需要多長時間提升技能的更多資訊見〖角色發展〗章節，p. <span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span>。同時該特質使任何長期專案的基礎時間增加了50％。至愛親朋還會帶來其他方面的障礙，礙手礙腳、分享生活空間、牽涉角色工作、借車、在最不恰當的時候打來電話等等。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>業力，至愛親朋是偶爾的麻煩：意外拜訪（比如說，當角色一定要去和誰碰頭的時候），需要情感支援，好感，其他友誼或承擔義務的見證以及偶爾的一點錢。這個級別的至愛親朋的例子包括：懶惰的兄弟姐妹，長期男女朋友，一個雖然角色不和他住在一起卻為之支付撫養費並定期探視的孩子。提高角色每個月生活花銷<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>％。</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>業力，至愛親朋會帶來經常的不便：需要關注以及承擔定期的義務，參與角色的事務，分享生活空間。這個級別的至愛親朋的例子包括：一個未婚同居的情人、妻子、丈夫或家庭成員，一個角色分享其撫養權並定期到訪他家的孩子（每隔一個週末等），角色負責的幼兒或親密的兄弟姐妹。提高角色每個月生活花銷<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>％。</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>業力，至愛親朋是和角色生活在一起的親密家人或生活伴侶：至愛親朋讓角色的時間和資源都變得緊張，甚至需要特殊的照顧和關注，這限制了角色可能的任務和具體行動。這些至愛親朋的例子包括分享生活空間的大家庭，需要醫護的父母或祖父母，任何其擁有完全撫養權的孩子。提高角色每個月生活花銷<span lang=\"EN-US\">30%</span>。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 82"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"X5NHxow8m0aYAmCU"}
{"name":"註冊者（分級）（SINner (Layered)）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>到<span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　在此劣勢中，註冊者共分四類：國家認證，犯罪者認證（公司或國家任一），公司受限認證，或公司歸屬認證。基於法律，經過認證的個人應時刻保持認證資訊的公開透明。身份經過合法認證是一應合法交易的前提。這讓身份認證顯得尤為重要，因此未經認證者通常會使用〖假SIN〗（p. <span lang=\"EN-US\">367</span>），以此混跡于正常社會體系。</span><em><strong>（譯註：下文中的「認證」均代指<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIN；編注：Sinner有個「罪人」的雙關在裡面，不過想不到合適的譯法，特此一提，也求建議</span>）</strong></em></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">國家認證<span lang=\"EN-US\"> NATIONAL SIN</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">　　在此分級中，角色因身份認證獲得<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>業力，該身份認證被稱為國家認證。角色的父母是國家的合法公民（比如<span lang=\"EN-US\">UCAS</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">CAS</span>），自出生以來他也一直是這個國家的公民。他擁有選舉權，有資格獲得國家頒發的護照，可應徵入伍，或在政府機關工作。對於獲取國家安全許可證或任何形式的國家軍事職業，國家身份認證都是不可或缺的。經過國家認證的角色須繳納<span lang=\"EN-US\">15%</span>的收入作為所得稅。他也絕無可能與任何超級公司產生瓜葛。擁有一個合法的身份認證主要的缺點在於角色身處體系之內。玩家角色背景中的母國擁有角色的生物識別數據（<span lang=\"EN-US\">DNA</span>，指紋，視網膜掃瞄）檔案，且這些識別數據將通過全球認證登記處與執法機構共享。這使得追蹤一個誤入歧途的角色變得易如反掌。同樣的，國家會把通過身份認證獲取的角色個人資訊出售給公司。因此，一個擁有合法身份的角色收到的垃圾郵件近三倍于身份未經認證者或假身份使用者，且這些郵件往往異乎尋常的符合他們的偏好（基於他們的購物與瀏覽習慣）。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">犯罪者認證<span lang=\"EN-US\"> CRIMINAL SIN</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">　　在此分級中，角色因身份認證獲得<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力，該身份認證被稱為犯罪者認證（公司或國家任一）；不管他過去擁有何種身份認證，現如今都已被犯罪者認證取代。在角色人生中的某段時間，他曾被拘捕並作為重刑犯服刑，此後他的餘生都會背上犯罪者的烙印。基於法律，他的犯罪者認證應時刻保持公開透明；如若不然將以重罪論處，並被押解勞改。他會被法治社會排斥。如果守法公民別無選擇，他們寧可與未經身份認證者打交道，也不願與犯罪者扯上關係。因他是戴罪之身，角色會飽受來自絕大多數守法公民的偏見、懷疑，甚至是公開的敵意。某些場所（高檔商店，汽車經銷店，博物館，畫廊等）總會對他關上大門，想找份合法的工作也頗有難度。若他所在的地區發生犯罪事件，他或被在任何時間帶走問詢，最長可達<span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span>小時。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2075</span>年的司法體系與其說是司法機構，不如說更像是條流水線。除非能證明清白，嫌疑犯會被視為有罪，那些似是而非的間接證據總能被用以定罪，量刑也常取決於法官的心情而非罪行。在這種大環境下，比起解決任何案件，警方也總是更傾向於快速結案；他們可能會試著把罪名推到有犯罪者認證的角色身上，無論她是否與案情有牽連。通過一定程度的「調整」事實與「解讀」證詞來馳援指控是常見的手段；僅為滿足定罪指標而偽造證據也不鮮見。對比普通罪犯，司法系統傾向於嚴厲處置魔法使用者。如果角色是個經過犯罪者認證的魔法使用者，這意味著他被地方執法部門登記在冊。他將會接受例行的非定時檢查以確認他是否健在，並確認他是否使用了違禁的術式，法器或其他魔法器具。為角色登記犯罪者認證的國家或公司會嚴密監控他，若他未能及時反饋居住資訊或以任何方式企圖逃避監管，將因此受到拘捕。他還應向認證機構繳納收入的<span lang=\"EN-US\">15%</span>作為所得稅。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">公司受限認證<span lang=\"EN-US\"> CORPORATE LIMITED SIN</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">　　在此分級中，角色因身份認證獲得<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>業力，該身份認證被稱為公司受限認證；他設法從外部在一家超級公司中謀得了一個職位。他可能被招為僱員（或是受聘員工的未成年子女），也可能因其在技術、能力、專業領域的才華或是其它亮點被公司中的某人相中。在絕大多數情況下，公司受限認證將取代其它國家認證。他的公司受限認證會被記入執法機構與保安公司皆可訪問的全球認證登記。這一類公司受限認證檔案中，有許多都會記錄角色是否為覺醒者。在絕大多數情況下，公司受限認證允許角色被超級公司僱傭，它能取代角色過去可能有的任何國家認證。憑藉公司認證，角色可被簽發認證的超級公司以員工、低階警衛或公司私兵的身份高薪聘用。即便他可以獲得機密級安全許可證以履行他的職責，他也無法升至領導層、成為官員或是超級公司特種部隊的一員（例如赤紅武士）。作為一個團隊，認證了公司受限身份的角色們被認為知道一些關於大型公司內部運轉情況的寶貴情報，或擁有能令公司競爭對手覬覦的特長；因此即便他們不再活躍于公司中，也仍會成為挖角對象。擁有公司受限認證的角色會受到來自陰影中未經認證者的偏見與敵視。未經認證者相信他們的窮困是公司故意為之，以行其剝削之事。擁有公司受限認證的角色會發現，其他人可能會單方面將他所屬公司的行為歸咎於他&mdash;&mdash;即使申辯他無權決策且與那些行動無關，大多也無濟於事。對於未經認證者與新無政府主義者來說，持有公司受限認證的角色出賣了自己的靈魂，背棄人民選擇了一個腐敗壓迫的制度。角色會把總收入中的百分之二十作為所得稅繳納給他受雇的公司。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; color: #e84800; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">公司歸屬認證<span lang=\"EN-US\"> CORPORATE SIN</span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #ffc000;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"color: black;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟雅黑;\"> </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 微軟雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif'; mso-bidi-font-family: 細明體; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">　<span style=\"color: #000000;\">　</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span>業力的認證分級被稱為公司歸屬認證。擁有該身份的角色或出生於一家超級公司，或在這家公司獲得治外法權時為其工作。他父母中至少有一個同樣擁有公司所屬認證。他在公司中長大，他的社交、教育，以及生活中的方方面面全都由公司管控。他的技術與才能被時時評估，同時也會被以最適合他發展的方向來培養；公司就是他的全世界。持有公司歸屬認證的角色們有機會與可能在公司中獲得晉陞。他可以是部門管理、金融分析師、隸屬於公司情報機構的特工、公司私軍軍官，甚至是超級公司特種部隊的一員（如聯絡的赤紅武士或阿瑞斯的火伺）。因其公司歸屬認證，他能享受到公司內部最高機密許可的待遇，且有權使用幾乎無限的資源。然而天有不測風雲。或因犯下大錯、或被競爭對手陰謀陷害、或成高層的替罪羔羊&mdash;&mdash;種種原因將角色從公司中除名，捲入了冷酷無情的暗影之中。在暗影籠罩下，這種過去炙手可熱的身份認證如今卻成了致命的負累。絕大多數暗影中人將公司歸屬認證者視作少數特權階級，那些坐在防彈轎車裡依權仗勢俯視、欺壓、利用、拒絕他們的貴族們。若未經身份認證者發現角色的身份為公司歸屬認證，反應會從深懷戒心到暴力敵對，不一而足；這大有可能造成嚴重的傷害事件甚至死亡。角色對他的公司忠心不二，當他身處的群體反對該超級公司時，這一點會帶來不小的阻礙。曾有準狂奔者因持有公司歸屬認證被害的記錄。幸運的是，只有其所屬的超級公司記錄了這些身份檔案。她在全球身份登記處的檔案僅能確認其身份的有效性，但其中不包含任何額外資訊。公司歸屬認證者需向其公司繳納收入中的百分之十作為其所得稅。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 86"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"XUjo8tg4qW0ksW1D"}
{"name":"免疫系統衰弱（Weak Immune System）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt;\">免疫系統的衰弱會降低角色對感染和疾病的抵抗力。在抗病檢定中，所有疾病的強度＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>。選擇了免疫系統衰弱的角色無法選擇天生免疫或病原體<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>毒素抗力作為優勢。免疫系統的衰弱往往源於電子改造與基因改造中的免疫抑制處理，因此有理由相信角色中經過身體改造的個體更容易獲得這種劣勢。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 89"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"YWrsL8hUyF80jRXW"}
{"name":"應急機師（Juryrigger）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　應急機師給予了角色對機電裝置的內部運作和基本原則的直觀把握。她瞭解如何修理破壞、磨損，提高裝置效率以及做到那些設計者根本沒有打算的事情。擁有應急機師特質的角色在應急使用裝備時的專業技能檢定獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。（編注：專業技能的關聯屬性多數為邏輯，詳見<a>〖技能列表〗</a>章節）如果GM需要決定角色想要完成的事情有沒有可能，他可以參考她成功使用〖建造與修理〗（P. 146）的閾值，然後將這個檢定的閾值-1。成功的機械技能檢定能夠使應急機師展現驚人的技術專長，她所有的設計都是暫時性的。擁有應急機師特質的角色可以做到的事情包括：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>僅再一次使用一個已被摧毀的裝置（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1D6</span>分鐘）。</li>\n<li>在<span lang=\"EN-US\">1D6</span>個戰鬥輪內，調整電子裝置的功率，使裝置等級+1。</li>\n<li><span lang=\"EN-US\">在<span lang=\"EN-US\">1D6分鐘內</span>，</span>使載具或無人機的部件獲得暫時性的額外效能，使其感測器或操作＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>（如果結合機械腦袋的獎勵加值，載具或無人機的關鍵部件在超越界限的持續時間結束后將會完全熄火；這個時候，載具或無人機就和巨大的鎮紙無異）。</li>\n<li>用不同的部件組裝出臨時的一次性裝置或武器（ＧＭ決定哪些部件適用）。</li>\n<li>設計一種臨時方法繞過安全措施，例如安全犁或壓力板。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 77"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"Z8J7rHZtK00Exu1k"}
{"name":"失眠（Insomnia）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　一個擁有失眠特質的角色在入睡和休息上會有些麻煩。通常情況下，這只是個小煩惱。但對於狂奔者依賴每一個機會來休息以保持敏銳的狂奔者來說，這就是大問題了。失眠會延長角色恢復眩暈傷害的時間。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　在<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力這個等級上，角色在擲骰體質＋意志來恢復眩暈傷害前，需要通過直覺＋意志（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）檢定。如果角色檢定成功，角色不會受到失眠的妨礙並正常恢復眩暈傷害。他也可以在<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>個小時的睡眠后恢復１點極限。如果角色檢定失敗，角色恢復他們眩暈傷害的時間成為通常的雙倍。因此原本需要一個小時恢復的量，現在需要兩個小時。如果角色被失眠影響，他的極限點不會恢復而且也不會在接下來的<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>小時內恢復。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　在<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>業力這個等級上，直覺＋意志（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）檢定上的失敗意味著所有通過休息來恢復眩暈傷害的努力都白費了，角色只能稍後重試。經歷失眠的角色沒有恢復眩暈傷害，而且必須等待<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>小時才能恢復極限點。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 83"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"ZrZCtSgVGaazw8Zq"}
{"name":"精魂災星（Spirit Bane）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span></p>\n<p>　　擁有精魂災星的角色會令某種型別的精魂（第<span lang=\"EN-US\">303</span>頁）變得扭曲。也許是因為他們慣於傷害一類精魂，也許是因為某種讓精魂狂暴的體質，精魂宿敵在遇到這樣的角色時常常會阻擾她，它們可能會不願遵從或幫助該角色和其同夥。如果該型別的精魂受命去攻擊該角色所在的小隊，那些精魂會先把她提溜出來嘗試第一個幹掉。受影響的精魂總會死命對付那些有著精魂災星的角色。如果具有精魂災星的角色試圖召喚或約束這一類精魂，她的這一嘗試將受到<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池的減值。若召喚者嘗試放逐這一類精魂，該精魂將在這次對抗中獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池加值。監視靈（Watchers）和其他小鬼（Minion）不受這個特質影響，因為他們是被構造的而不是像普通精魂一樣被召喚的。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\">　　這種劣勢僅能為魔法使用者所選。他們可選擇與自身魔法流派無關的精魂類別作為精魂宿敵。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 87"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"buSKQPlhEEDHxfxG"}
{"name":"戰鬥麻痹（Combat Paralysis）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有戰鬥麻痹的角色在戰鬥中會呆住（也包括在矩陣戰鬥以及星界戰鬥的情況）。角色的第一次主動性檢定中，其主動性值減為一半（向上取整）。在隨後的戰鬥輪，角色可以如常投擲他們的主動性。戰鬥麻痹也讓角色在突襲檢定中承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">－3</span>骰池調整。如果角色必須在槍林彈雨中或類似的情況下進行沉著檢定，那麼檢定閾值＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 82"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"cas0MV2rS2BvZ8hW"}
{"name":"榮譽守則（Code of Honor）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　被榮譽守則約束的角色不會殺害某類特定的人；這是一個堅定的原則。擁有榮譽守則特質的角色選擇一類特定人群，他不會殺害這類人也不會允許別人去殺。這類例子包括婦女、兒童、無辜的旁觀者或特定種族。角色可以選擇去保護特定的生物，但僅限於這種特定生物擁有智慧。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">角色選擇的「禁區」需要ＧＭ的批準。如果這類群體（如兒童）在戰役中不常遇，ＧＭ拒絕這個選擇。如果玩家一定要選擇，ＧＭ可以允許玩家選擇兩個他不會傷害的群體（例如，婦女和兒童），其中之一必須在戰役中經常遇到。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">如果魔法使用者的精魂導師對某種精魂有增益，前者可以合理的選擇不摧毀該精魂。這種榮譽守則就是尊重他們的精魂導師，是值得業力的。（即，如果角色的精魂導師對某種精魂有增益，那麼他可以將那種精魂作為「不殺」群體）</p>\n<p align=\"left\">　　角色不能為這個特質選擇不起眼的或不存在的群體，例如你不會因為發誓絕不殺害智慧倉鼠而獲得業力獎勵。（「布布，讓他們在你正義的吶喊下顫抖吧！」「吱吱！」）</p>\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　任何時候任何人試圖殺害角色保護清單中的人時，這個角色必須通過魅力＋意志（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）檢定。失敗的擲骰意味著角色必須立刻阻止對其保護群體施加的暴力行為。如果形勢所迫，角色採取行動對抗他保護的群體，他通常會選擇非致命的凡事。他絕不會因為任何理由地殺害一名他發誓保護的群體成員。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　擁有榮譽守則會造成一些障礙。例如，可能留下目擊者。被角色保護的群體中每有一個人活著離開並記住了他，就提高一點角色的公眾認知。角色的工作選擇也受到限制，他不會選取那些目標是致死其保護群體一員的工作，他也會對於那些很可能對他保護的群體造成間接傷害的工作持保留意見。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　無論何時採用非致命武力都很可能出錯。一個人可能對通常無害的迷藥會有危及生命的過敏性反應，或者心臟的狀況讓泰瑟槍的電擊也會致死。因此，每次角色採取暴力行動或允許別人採取暴力行動對付他所選的群體時，ＧＭ就暗骰<span lang=\"EN-US\">1D6</span>，結果為<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>就導致使用非致命武力時出現不可預見狀況。泛人類在危及生命的醫療條件下，試圖驅逐精魂而不是摧毀之卻讓其獲得了自由。當這種複雜的問題出現時，ＧＭ為角色暗骰察覺（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）檢定來判斷角色是否注意到有什麼不對勁。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　如果角色選擇的群體中的人被殺，無論是有意還是無意，角色都會由於這種冒險中每一個被殺的他保護的人而失去一點業力。</p>\n<p>榮譽守則也可以有其他形式。例如：</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"left\">刺客信條（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Assassin</span>』<span lang=\"EN-US\">s Creed</span>）：無人買命，絕不殺之。作為一個刺客，不留下無謂的傷害，是相信刺客信條的人無形而重要的標誌。選取這種榮譽守則，每個意外或無償謀殺都會使其失去<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>點業力，每次這樣的死亡也會讓其名氣+1。</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">勇士守則（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Warrior</span>』<span lang=\"EN-US\">s Code</span>）：遵循一種勇士守則的角色嚴守個人榮譽。在<span lang=\"EN-US\">2075</span>年，這可能意味著角色不會殺害一個手無寸鐵的人，也不會對不知道他、沒準備好的敵人採取致命行動（例如，沒知道狂奔者在那的守衛），或有意採取行動殺害完全沒有防備的人（例如，流彈或允許狙擊斃命）。角色每殺死一個或允許通過他的行動殺死一個手無寸鐵或毫無防備的人就失去<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>點業力。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt;\">（譯註：擴<span lang=\"EN-US\">Run Faster</span>里有很多很有趣的榮譽守則，有興趣的可以看看）</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 81"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"e1ggFq1yu3nvOZQ0"}
{"name":"天生運動員（Natural Athlete）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有這個特質的角色有著與生俱來的身體素質、空間意識和天生的田徑或體操天賦的結合。角色也許不是世界級的運動員並且需要訓練才能達到巔峰，然而他擁有在他的體型和重量級下最佳身體狀態。天生運動員在奔跑和體操技能檢定上獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 78"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZNcgev6i3v1RXv8Z"}},"_id":"f6DynXTVt0xgXJem"}
{"name":"手抖（Unsteady Hands）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　手抖的角色的手部靈活性與精度會因輕微的抖動而受到影響。當這一癥狀發作時，角色任何基於敏捷的檢定將受到<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整。這種情況可能是由於生理（例如未經治療的遺傳病或神經損傷）、心理創傷，甚至年齡導致的。在通常情況下，某些改造或藥物能掩蓋這些癥狀。在緊張的狀況下，癥狀可能復發。角色在經歷了一段充滿壓力的遭遇后（例如搏鬥），需經過敏捷＋體質（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）檢定。檢定成功意味著該癥狀並未復發（僅限目前）。檢定失敗將會導致病癥復發，且會持續至故事結束。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 89"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"feH9Xqfk73zejX3S"}
{"name":"無能力（Incompetent）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　一個無能力的角色完全缺乏對一些一些行動技能組的能力和知識。更糟的是，他們可能具備一點模糊的知識和相關技能，但他們既沒有協調能力也沒有理解能力使之正確發揮作用。無論他們在這個領域投入多少努力，他們都不得要領。也許某天在某種程度上發生了奇蹟，他們在這些技能上進步到「低劣」的水平。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　無能力不適用于語言或知識技能。無能力的角色在相關技能組所有技能上視為「無知」（見〖技能等級表〗，p. <span lang=\"EN-US\">131</span>）。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　某些情況下，對於大多數人來說司空見慣的任務於他們需要一個成功的檢定。角色不能嘗試他們為無能力特質選擇的技能組。即便裝備為角色無能力相關的特定技能提供了獎勵，角色也不能在該裝備上獲益。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　在實際遊戲中，ＧＭ完全可拒絕與無能力特質不相關或壓榨性的選擇，比如無能力：完全基於一個理想城市的戶外戰役。（不該這麼說，但只能用這個例子：角色不能選擇任何他們身體上完全不能使用的技能組。一個非魔法師不能為無能力選擇巫術、咒法或附魔；一個非超鏈者不能為無能力選擇關聯共鳴的技能等等。）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　無能力只能被購買一次。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 83"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"fjMYUjmUQUjVwZPN"}
{"name":"第一印象（First Impression）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　第一印象特質使一個角色可以輕鬆融入新的環境、處境、群體和工作中。無論是滲透進一個幫派、在新的城市找到關係還是在一次私人會面中的爭論，角色在第一次會面中有關社交檢定上獲得臨時＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整，如談判和欺騙。這個調整值不適用于第二次以及隨後的遭遇。此外，這個特質會使惡名-1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 76"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"g29Yu2RidkXWOVLU"}
{"name":"雙關節（Double-Jointed）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　一個有雙關節的角色擁有非常靈活的關節，可以將他的身體彎曲到極致。角色在脫逃術檢定上獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。角色可以擠進普通人無法進入的狹小空間。他們也很擅長在派對和酒吧之類的場合發揮。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"mEk7ZK7hG4JwGHz4"}
{"name":"粗魯（Uncouth）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有粗魯劣勢的角色很難與他人良好互動。他行事衝動，對任何自認的挑釁行為反應過度，且傾向於把任何突如其來的念頭付諸行動而不計後果（例：做下流的手勢，管一個醉巨魔叫「巨傻」，或是以有情破顏拳來回應競爭對手的閑話）。所有角色用以抵抗行為不當或衝動的社交檢定要承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池的減值。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　此外，粗魯的角色用以學習或提高社交技能的業力花費是通常情況下的兩倍（包括角色建立環節），且他們可能永遠也學不到任何社交技能組。那些粗魯的角色不具備等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>或更高等級的社交技能被視作無知水平（見技能等級，第<span lang=\"EN-US\">129</span>頁）。即使是那些對普通角色來說不成問題的社交情境，<span lang=\"EN-US\">GM</span>也可以要求角色為其進行檢定。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 87"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"mpKxYOuwRnQ2ZuKr"}
{"name":"雙母語（Bilingual）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　擁有這個特質的角色可以流利地讀、寫、講第二門語言。他們可以選擇第二門語言作為母語（見語言技能，<span lang=\"EN-US\">P150</span>）。這個特質只能在角色建立時選取；選擇該特質讓角色在第五步：購買行動、知識和語言技能（<span lang=\"EN-US\">P88</span>）中獲得第二個免費語言技能。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 74"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"n8V1mbdWikMl86Jl"}
{"name":"集中專注（Focused Concentration）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：每等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>業力（最大<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>級）</p>\n<p>　　一個擁有集中專注特質的超鏈者或魔法使用者經過了訓練從而可能比其他人在操縱魔力或共鳴上更加精確。這種精確減少了對魔法使用者或超鏈者身體的壓力。她能夠維持一個強度<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>等級等於她的集中專注等級的法術<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>複合程式，無需承受任何懲罰。例如，一個擁有等級３集中專注的魔法使用者可以維持強度<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>的『護甲術』而不用在維持法術時承受負面骰池調整。維持任何額外法術或複合程式都受到標準的每維持一個法術或複雜形式<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整。這個特質只能被能夠施法的魔法使用者和超鏈者角色選擇。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 76"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"pA2iBvXBpeISB9mL"}
{"name":"高度耐痛（High Pain Tolerance）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：每等級<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>業力（最大<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>級）</p>\n<p>　　高度耐痛能讓角色在已經承受了不少疼痛的情況下還能繼續承受疼痛。在計算傷害調整時（見傷害調整，<span lang=\"EN-US\">P169</span>），擁有高度耐痛的角色可以忽略每等級一點傷害。因此，擁有這個特質<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>級的角色可以承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>點傷害而沒有傷害調整，就如同他只受了<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>點傷害。當這個角色受到第五點傷害時，立刻承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">－1</span>傷害調整。該特質不會與『疼痛抗力』修士異能，&lt;痛感編輯器&gt;生體改造，或&lt;傷害代償器&gt;生體改造同時生效。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 76"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"pqkEhjNxkjx9D0lK"}
{"name":"機械腦袋（Gearhead）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　機械腦袋是你需要猛踩油門立刻閃人的時候最需要的人。她是天生的司機或飛行員。當她在載具或無人機的車輪、搖桿或控制器上時，她能夠直觀瞭解機器的侷限和能力並且操作其到最佳狀態。在載具或飛車戰鬥中，機械腦袋可以使其載具/無人機的速度/操控性＋１（玩家決定），持續1D6分鐘。她在載具中嘗試困難動作或特技時，也能獲得＋<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>骰池調整。這個獎勵持續<span lang=\"EN-US\">1D6</span>分鐘。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　玩家如果願意可以選擇再獲得額外的<span lang=\"EN-US\">1D6</span>分鐘獎勵。這樣做會使載具或無人機超過其設計極限並有災難性傷害的風險。角色每讓載具獲得獎勵超過初始獎勵一分鐘，載具就會自動受到一點壓力傷害<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>不能抵抗<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 76"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"pvNrZFKx8ZmyRixs"}
{"name":"壞運氣（Bad Luck）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p align=\"left\">獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>業力</p>\n<p align=\"left\">這個角色被詛咒了，他的運氣常常和他自己作對。當角色使用極限，擲骰<span lang=\"EN-US\">1D6</span>。結果為<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>，則極限點被花費但獲得同預期相反的效果。在這次遭遇中，角色承受了壞運氣的影響后，他就不需要再次為極限擲骰壞運氣檢定。以下為幾個壞運氣的例子：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>界限突破（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Push the Limit</span>）：不再獲得骰池加值，反而要承受數值相同的骰池減值。</li>\n<li>動如迅雷（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Blitz</span>）：主動性骰變為<span lang=\"EN-US\">+0D6</span>，這意味著他只有自己的主動性屬性作為主動性值計算。</li>\n<li>先機在握（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Seize the Initiative</span>）：你被移到主動性順序的最後一位。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"left\">注意，這個特質會使惡名<span lang=\"EN-US\">+1</span>。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 81"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"sQoX0LiA99Ns5zNQ"}
{"name":"壞名聲（Bad Rep）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　擁有壞名聲特質的角色在她的名譽中有個黑暗而持久的污點。她可能是個前遊俠條子，衆所周知她處理暗影狂奔者時非常殘酷。或者道上傳聞她可能曾經殺害了她狂奔者團隊中的同伴。如果她是覺醒者並來自污染區，那可能被普遍認為是一名毒薩滿。她是否真的犯下了這樣的罪行並沒有什麼關係。當人們相信她曾經的所作所為就決定了角色如何看待她，如何對待她。無論什麼原因，角色開始遊戲時擁有<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>點惡名（<span lang=\"EN-US\">P372</span>），只有解決了損壞名譽的源頭才能取消或減少這個點數。只有這樣，壞名聲特質方可被用業力購買后取消效果。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 81"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"toOPfV7b0fQkrXRn"}
{"name":"雙巧手（Ambidextrous）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>花費：４業力</p>\n<p>　　雙巧手角色的雙手使用東西能夠一樣靈巧。沒有這個特質，任何僅用副手進行的行動（例如，開槍）承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>骰池調整（見「攻擊者使用副手武器」，p. <span lang=\"EN-US\">178</span>）。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 73"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":null,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"positive"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"uqeiIMwu2oanWuz3"}
{"name":"裝作精靈（Elf Poser）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>業力</p>\n<p>　　裝作精靈就是那些想要成為精靈的人類角色。她儘可能地與精靈交往，像精靈一樣說話，把自己的外貌打扮得像一個精靈。擁有這個特質的角色可能會接受整容手術做出精靈耳朵和眼睛，他們能夠如精靈一樣成功通過同時避免作為非精靈的任何負面社交調整。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　真正的精靈認為裝作精靈令人尷尬，很多人類把他們當作背叛者，其他泛人類一般覺得他們很可憐。如果一個精靈發現了角色的秘密，這個精靈很可能用蔑視和敵意對待她（見〖社交調整表〗，<span lang=\"EN-US\">P140</span>）。帶有偏見的人類很可能將一個被揭露的裝作精靈視為「種族叛徒」來羞辱。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">　　只有人類角色可以選取裝作精靈特質。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 83"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"y0rhIQOjNTEEgDvK"}
{"name":"腦灼傷（Scorched）","type":"quality","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">獎勵：<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>業力</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　一個腦灼傷的角色正在應付一些神經問題，這些問題是由於某些方式如黑<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>、變態<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>造成的傷害引起的。這些問題可能表現爲短期或長期記憶喪失、大腦突然空白、頻繁的偏頭痛、感官能力減弱（視覺、觸覺、嗅覺等），以及如偏執和焦慮這樣的情緒障礙。玩家為腦灼傷選擇一個特定效果，其效果應該明顯到足以阻礙角色並與ＧＭ目前安排的伏筆掛鉤。每當他進入<span lang=\"EN-US\">VR</span>或插上一片<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>，角色就必須通過一個體質＋意志（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）的檢定。擲骰失敗，他就會經歷六個小時這種特定的物理影響。這個檢定中的失誤或大失誤將導致受影響的時間長達<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>小時。消除腦灼傷特質的唯一辦法就是獲得必要的修復損傷治療，然後花費業力把負面特質去掉。然而一旦腦灼傷，角色會依舊容易受到環境影響。另一個糟糕的事情是使用黑<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>、精神<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>將會導致這個特質復發。角色除了腦灼傷時肉體上遭受的副作用，他還容易受到黑<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>、變態<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>的傷害。當面對這些<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>，角色必須通過一個沉著檢定（4）來判斷是否處變不驚。如果他能面對造成他腦灼傷的<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>，角色在遭受這些程式造成的傷害時，傷害抗力承受<span lang=\"EN-US\">－2</span>調整。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　如果要選擇<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>的腦灼傷特質，角色必須至少對<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>有輕度成癮並且擁有使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">BTL</span>的裝備。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\">　　如果要選擇黑<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>或變態<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>的腦灼傷特質，角色必須是一名碟客或超鏈者。注意，這個特質會使惡名+1。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt;\" align=\"left\">（譯註：變態<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Psychotropic IC</span>，屬於黑<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>的一種。與普通的燒腦黑<span lang=\"EN-US\">IC</span>不同&mdash;&mdash;嗯，字面意義上的燒腦&mdash;&mdash;它能改變你的大腦結構，重寫你的思維，故取此譯。這是<span lang=\"EN-US\">SR 3e</span>里的一個設定，目前在<span lang=\"EN-US\">5e</span>里還沒見到有相關資料）<s></s></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: '微軟雅黑','sans-serif';\"> </span></p>\n<table style=\"width: 454pt;\" border=\"0\" width=\"604\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\"><colgroup> <col style=\"width: 16pt; mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 672;\" width=\"21\" /> <col style=\"width: 99pt; mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 4224;\" width=\"132\" /> <col style=\"width: 323pt; mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 13760;\" width=\"430\" /> <col style=\"width: 16pt; mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 672;\" width=\"21\" /> </colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.5pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl77\" style=\"height: 32.25pt; width: 454pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" colspan=\"4\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"604\" height=\"43\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffc000; font-size: x-large;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #ffc000; font-size: x-large;\">腦灼傷生理副作用表</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.75pt; mso-height-source: userset;\"></tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.25pt;\">\n<td class=\"xl65\" style=\"height: 17.25pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"23\"><span style=\"color: #ffc000;\">　</span></td>\n<td class=\"xl64\" style=\"border-top: #ffc000 1pt solid; border-right: #f0f0f0; border-bottom: #ffc000 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: black;\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffc000;\">效果</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl76\" style=\"border-top: #ffc000 1pt solid; border-right: #f0f0f0; border-bottom: #ffc000 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: black;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffc000;\">遊戲規則</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl68\" style=\"border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: black;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffc000;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 72pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"height: 72pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"96\">　</td>\n<td class=\"xl67\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">短期記憶喪失</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl72\" style=\"width: 323pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"430\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">角色不記得插入了一片BTL晶片。角色立即進行另一次戒斷檢定。失敗意味著渴望立即再次到來，這作為戒斷癥狀。角色必須插入另一片晶片。如果是IC，角色必須通過一個閾值＋1的記憶檢定。失敗導致記憶的裂縫，甚至可能迷失在主機中。</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"height: 54pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"72\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">　</span></td>\n<td class=\"xl71\" style=\"background-color: #404040; border: #f0f0f0;\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">長期記憶喪失</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl73\" style=\"width: 323pt; background-color: #404040; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"430\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">與短期記憶喪失效果相同。另外，在效果持續期間，角色失去使用一個行動技能的能力。他單純記不得如何使用了（例如，手槍技能）。將這個技能視為未受訓直到癥狀消失。</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"height: 36pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"48\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">　</span></td>\n<td class=\"xl67\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">大腦突然空白</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl72\" style=\"width: 323pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"430\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">在效果持續期間，角色對這段時間裡的事情沒有記憶。這些記憶不能被技術或魔法的手段恢復。</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"height: 18pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"24\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">　</span></td>\n<td class=\"xl71\" style=\"background-color: #404040; border: #f0f0f0;\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">偏頭痛</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl73\" style=\"width: 323pt; background-color: #404040; border: #f0f0f0;\" width=\"430\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">角色在所有肉體和精神檢定上承受－2，對光敏感且噁心（P409）。</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54pt; mso-height-source: userset;\">\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"height: 54pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"72\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">　</span></td>\n<td class=\"xl75\" style=\"border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; border-bottom: #ffc000 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: black;\">\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">偏執、焦慮</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"xl74\" style=\"border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: #f0f0f0; width: 323pt; border-bottom: #ffc000 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; background-color: black;\" width=\"430\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2; font-size: small;\">即使基礎社交活動，角色也必須通過社交檢定。成功閾值為5。如果沒有合適的技能，角色預設魅力－1。失敗意味著角色在這種場合下會表現得偏執或焦慮。</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.25pt;\">\n<td class=\"xl70\" style=\"height: 17.25pt; background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\" height=\"23\">　</td>\n<td class=\"xl69\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">　</span></td>\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">　</span></strong></td>\n<td class=\"xl66\" style=\"background-color: black; border: #f0f0f0;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #f2f2f2;\">　</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","source":"SR5E 85"},"action":{"type":"","category":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","spec":"","mod":0,"mod_description":"","limit":{"value":0,"base":0,"attribute":""},"extended":false,"damage":{"type":{"value":"","base":""},"element":{"value":"","base":""},"value":0,"base":0,"ap":{"value":0,"base":0},"base_formula_operator":"add","attribute":"","itemSource":{"actorId":"","itemId":"","itemType":"","itemName":""}},"opposed":{"type":"","attribute":"","attribute2":"","skill":"","mod":0,"description":""}},"type":"negative"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lOz6oFsrM4wdNgO0":3},"flags":{},"_id":"zyUtC6Z67R27lwRa"}
